"{\"uid\": \"news.cgtn.com-news-2024-04-17-100-days-to-go-Exploring-Paris-2024-in-figures-1sRQyI8AamA-p.html\", \"text\": \"Our Privacy Statement & Cookie Policy  By continuing to browse our site you agree to our use of cookies, revised Privacy Policy and Terms of Use. You can change your cookie settings through your browser.  CGTN  Copied  The first Olympics with an equal gender split among athletes, the second city to host the Summer Olympics three times after London, 19 days of competition, 35 venues,\\u00a0329 medal events spanning 32 sports, 10,500 athletes, 20,000 accredited journalists and 31,500 volunteers. These figures offer a glimpse into the grandeur of the Paris 2024 Olympic Games as the 100-day countdown commences.  The figures only refer to the Paris 2024 Olympic Games.  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466  SITEMAP  EXPLORE MORE  DOWNLOAD OUR APP  Copyright \\u00c2\\u00a9 2024 CGTN.\\u00e4\\u00ba\\u00acICP\\u00e5\\u00a4\\u008720000184\\u00e5\\u008f\\u00b7  Disinformation report hotline: 010-85061466\"}"